        {
            "title": "安能物流下午復牌  私有化要約仍存不確定性",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">安能物流(09956)公布，有關大鉦資本與淡馬錫私有化公司的建議，仍存不確定性，股份下午復牌。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">公布稱，截至今天(10月17日)，大鉦資本持有公司24.32%股份，淡馬錫未持有任何股份。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">公司於2025年9月17日收到由大鉦資本及淡馬錫及旗下淡明資本財團的私有化建議。公司隨即申請股份停牌，該停牌自2025年9月18日上午9時正起生效，於今天公告日，大鉦資本持有公司2.86億股普通股，佔已發行股份總數約24.32%，淡馬錫及淡明資本並無持有任何股份。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">就收購守則而言，要約期自本公告日期（即2025年10月17日）開始。公布稱，董事會仍在考慮指示性收購建議，但指示性收購建議的談判結果仍存在不確定性，且無法確定指示性收購建議最終是否會導致就股份作出要約。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15350183-%e5%ae%89%e8%83%bd%e7%89%a9%e6%b5%81%e4%b8%8b%e5%8d%88%e5%be%a9%e7%89%8c-%e7%a7%81%e6%9c%89%e5%8c%96%e8%a6%81%e7%b4%84%e4%bb%8d%e5%ad%98%e4%b8%8d%e7%a2%ba%e5%ae%9a%e6%80%a7",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251017_FI_09956_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-17 13:05:22",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "津上精密機床預告半年溢利升48%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">津上精密機床(01651)盈喜，預告截至2025年9月30日止6個月公司擁有人應佔溢利約5.02億元(人民幣‧下同)，按年增48%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"公司年報\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/760x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251017_FI_01651_.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"公司年報\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/760x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251017_FI_01651_.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">公司年報</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">2024年9月30日止公司擁有人應佔溢利3.4億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">公布稱，業績增長受益於國內經濟的持續恢復。中國製造業的轉型升級，特別是新能源汽車、人工智能等用戶領域的快速發<br/>  展，給機床行業帶來了新的需求，以及公司近年對製造業各細分行業的持續開拓和滲透。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15350043-%e6%b4%a5%e4%b8%8a%e7%b2%be%e5%af%86%e6%a9%9f%e5%ba%8a%e9%a0%90%e5%91%8a%e5%8d%8a%e5%b9%b4%e6%ba%a2%e5%88%a9%e5%8d%8748",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251017_FI_01651_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-17 12:45:20",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "半日收市｜港股半日挫415點近低位收市   蘋概及光伏股瀉",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股接近半日低位收市，收跌415點，蘋概股及光伏股大挫，黃金相關股逆市升。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數半日收報25472，跌415點或1.6%，今早開跌36點或0.14%，報25821，早段見25859，跌29點或0.11%，為半日高位，跌幅隨即急速擴大，臨近收市低見25469，挫419點或1.62%，為半日低位。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：比亞迪電子官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241119_FI_source-web_00285-3-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：比亞迪電子官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241119_FI_source-web_00285-3-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：比亞迪電子官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：信義光能官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230719-123531_source-web_信義光能00968-1_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：信義光能官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230719-123531_source-web_信義光能00968-1_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：信義光能官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：周大福官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508011_FI_source-web_01929-2.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：周大福官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508011_FI_source-web_01929-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：周大福官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：比亞迪電子官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241119_FI_source-web_00285-3-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：比亞迪電子官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：信義光能官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230719-123531_source-web_信義光能00968-1_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：信義光能官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：周大福官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508011_FI_source-web_01929-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：周大福官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數半日跌168點或2.81%，報5835點，今早開跌4點或0.07%，報5999。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生國企指數半日跌155點或1.67%，報9104，今早開報9259點，無升跌。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指報25466，跌439點或1.7%，低水7點 ; 科指期貨報5837，跌184點或3.06%，高水2點 ; 國指期貨跌163點或1.76%，報9101，低水3點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交1531.72億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股開市後跌勢加劇，港股隨之下滑，美國爆地區銀行股災，此外內地周一公布第三季經濟增長，投行預期增長較前兩季放緩。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：比亞迪電子官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241119_FI_source-web_00285-3-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：比亞迪電子官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241119_FI_source-web_00285-3-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：比亞迪電子官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">手機設備股跑輸大市，比亞迪電子(00285)挫6.57%，報38.38元，為表現最差藍籌股 ; 舜宇光學科技(02382)跌3.67%，報77.4元 ; 丘鈦科技(01478)大瀉9.15%，報13.6元 ; 高偉電子(01415)跌4.88%，報31/56元。蘋果公司傳計劃2026年底或2027年初推出配備觸控螢幕的升級版MacBook Pro，放棄「蘋果教主」喬布斯（Steve Jobs）反對豎直觸控螢幕電腦的立場。喬布斯2012年時曾表示觸控螢幕不應是豎直的，而整個行業在十多年前就開始推出觸屏版筆記型電腦。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">光伏股下挫，內地傳聞多晶硅收儲平台已成立，信義光能(00968)半日跌5.43%，報3.48元，跌幅藍籌股中居第二位 ; 協鑫科技(03800)跌6.52%，報1.29元 ; 福萊特玻璃(06865)跌2.86%，報11.22元。今日突然有消息指，多晶硅收儲平台已經成立，平台公司工商註冊完成，名稱為「中硅產能整合有限公司」，共管帳號也已開立，將推行「以大收小」。官方媒體《證券時報》引述業內權威人士指出，該傳聞消息不實。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：信義光能官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230719-123531_source-web_信義光能00968-1_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：信義光能官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230719-123531_source-web_信義光能00968-1_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：信義光能官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金價上報4300美元，金礦股相關股揚升，周大福(01929)升4.39%，報16.42元，為表現最佳藍籌股 ; 六福(00590)升3.07%，報26.18元。金礦股升幅後段收窄，紫金黃金國際(02259)升2.92%，報151.7元 ; 紫金(02899)轉跌0.42%，報32.88元 ; 山東黃金(01787)升2.65%，報38.8元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：周大福官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508011_FI_source-web_01929-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：周大福官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508011_FI_source-web_01929-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：周大福官網</p>\n</a>\n</div>",
