            "title": "A股下挫  深股跌近2%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股早段報跌，深股跌近2%，創板近2.4%，兩市成交合計11795.6億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20150819_FI_AShare_4-2_source-ap_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20150819_FI_AShare_4-2_source-ap_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指半日報3877點，跌30點或1%，今早開報3912點，跌4點或0.1%，最高見3921，升5點或0.13%，隨即向下，低見3875點，跌41點或1.05%，為半日低位，半日成交5298.58億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指半日報12825點，挫260點或1.99%，開報13060，跌26點或0.2%，早段見13091，升5點或0.04%，其後轉跌，低見12820，瀉266點或2.03%，半日成交6497.02億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300半日跌58點或1.27%，報4559，今早開報4610，跌8點或0.17%，</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數半日跌71點或2.37%，報2965點，今早開報3026，跌11點或0.36%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">下周一內地公布第三季生產總值。</p>\n</div>",
